        /// loosed the focus.
        /// Callback int function(Ihandle *ih); [in C] ih:getfocus_cb() -> (ret:
        /// number) [in Lua] ih: identifier of the element that received keyboard focus.
        /// Affects All elements with user interaction, except menus.
